    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a definitive analog masterpiece. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a pristine Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Every critical failure point has been preemptively addressed: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, the VANOS system overhauled with uprated components, and rod bearings replaced with treated shells. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, utilizing original-spec Sachs dampers for that signature balance of compliance and lateral grip. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing no signs of track use or environmental degradation. This is a turn-key, mechanically synchronized machine for the discerning driver who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
